    "summary": "The user asks if it is safe to consume a small amount of alcohol while taking metronidazole for a tooth infection. The assistant initially provides dangerous advice by suggesting that one or two glasses of wine are acceptable, incorrectly dismissing the severity of the disulfiram-like reaction associated with this specific medication-alcohol interaction.",
